name: Robert Venable
bio: EMMY winning (3x), GRAMMY nominated music producer, mixer, and engineer. Kelly Clarkson, Twenty One Pilots, Megadeth, Disciple, MuteMath, etc…

This reverb unit is one of my absolute favorites for vocal plates. It also makes me want to play GameBoy!! 😂 

#lexicon #reverb #musicmixer

These @alclairaudio in-ear monitors go with me everywhere. ✈️ 

#iem #alclair #musicmixer

It’s a busy day, but I always have a few minutes to hang out with this little guy. 

#frenchie #frenchiesofinstagram #gaston
I spent the morning out here with my daughter who was shooting a music video. Not mad about the view! 🌲

Man, I love the way this guitar sounds! I’m not a guitar player at all, but there’s something about this one that sings to me.  I keep it in Drop D tuning, and default to “Southtown” by @pod (one of the only songs I can play). What’s your go-to song when you pick up a guitar? 

#guitar #notaguitarist #recordingstudio #pod #fender

Excited to be behind the kit again. (Throwback to 2014??)
#imtoooldforthis #drummer #deums

Here’s a blast from the past! Throwback to 2016… @travisbarker is one of the best drummers, ever. His playing influenced a lot of what I do: drum tones, musicality, and the notes between the notes. 

#travisbarker #blink182 #drummer

The pole, the feast, the airing of grievances and the feats of strength. 

Happy Festivus!

#seinfeld #festivus #featsofstrength

Oh, the places we’ll go. First stop, snare drum! 

I picked up this beauty from @byrdfinds in Nashville. 

#md441 #microphone #sennheiser #recordingstudio
Anniversary date night! ♥️

Smooth game vs NOT smooth game, by @manscaped. 😂 😝 🎉 

Ring in the new year as smooth as possible!

#MANSCAPED #hny #ad #2023

Happy Friday! Who’s being creative?

#compressor #rackgear
Jumping into 2023 with the faders up! Mixing music for broadcast is fun, different, and still very creative.

Don’t get me wrong, I LOVE recording and mixing on large format consoles, but you don’t NEED them to make good music.  People who know, what are some albums recorded or mixed in a bedroom, basement, or garage?

#api #mixingboard #recordingstudio #homestudio

Everyday’ as party with this console. 

#musicmixer #recordingstudio #digico

Work mode! 👊🏻 

“You should smile more” 

This IS me smiling. :) 

#meanmuggin #mix #studiolife

Audix D6s on toms, all day every day.  It’s like they come pre-EQed right out of the box. 

@audixmics

I have 2 spots on the lunchbox to fill. What should I get? Any hidden gems? What do you have?

#500series #lunchbox #recordingstudio #homestudio

Bourbon is my valentine.

Well, that, and my wife. And she’s the one who had this shirt made for me! Bourbon and my wife are my valentines. 

#valentine #bourbon #wife

Just a boy and his toys. Expensive toys. Toys he wishes were his, so they’re really someone else’s toys.

Also, they’re not toys. 

#recordingstudio #studiolife #faderfriday

Mixing the Lainey Wilson performance for The Kelly Clarkson Show, from my home studio. I’m happy for this blessing to be able to work remotely, at times. 

#heartlikeatruck #laineywilson #musicmixer #homestudio @laineywilsonmusic

The @locomotiveaudio 14b is ridiculous on vocals, especially paired with the API pres. Gooooooodness. 

#compressor #recordingstudio #musicmixer #recordingengineer @thisisapiaudio

I’m thankful for the opportunity to share what I know with people who are willing to learn.  Showcasing the @thisisapiaudio AXS console at @websteru while mixing a rock band in a room full of creatively-charged students. 
#rockmusic #recordingstudio #api @thedavegarret

Make sure the mic you’re using fits the singer and fits the song. Just because you have an expensive mic, it doesn’t mean it’s the one you have to use. I could’ve used (and might have preferred) a @shure sm7b on this session, but this mic sounded phenomenal, too! 

#mic #microphone #recordingstudio #musicmixer

So I like pushing snare drums a little loud, sue me. @lesterestelle hits hard most of the time, but not with brushes. This was tasty, can’t wait for you to hear it! 

#audix #faderfriday #dontspamme #musicmixer @audixmics @digico.official

I don’t think the folks at @digico.official would be thrilled with my feet being on the console. Sorry!! 

#jordan1 #kickstagram #digico #musicmixer

Maybe sometimes I need to have TWO Kensington trackballs. 🖲️ 

Rocking the Kensington SlimBlade Pro (I travel with it) during Kelly Clarkson rehearsals this weekend.  It’s familiar, it’s quick, and I like it. 

#trackball #recordingengineer #kellyclarkson #mixguy @rockpopsus

Today’s “recording studio.” I don’t take my job for granted, ever. It’s Kelly Clarkson’s birthday, and I have the privilege of recording her singing in this beautiful venue, tonight. 

#kellyclarkson #belasco #musicmixer #dreamjob

I don’t know whether to feel special or targeted. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯ 

Kelly Clarkson’s birthday at the Belasco concert was a blast… y’all aren’t ready for the new album, it’s so good!

#chemistry #kellyclarkson #newmusic #ninjaneer

Eleven. 

The show is nominated for 11 Emmys, this year! I work with the most talented and kind team of professionals who all work together to make this happen. 

Honored to be a small part of this team, and hope to bring home my third Emmy 🤯 

I was going to tag everyone but I know I’d miss several people.

Let’s talk about editing vocals. 😮 

Before I even start mixing, I start by editing the lead vocals: cutting dead space, addressing breaths and plosives, gain staging, time aligning, and crossfades. 

It takes time, but worth it. 

#musicmixer #vocals #protools #editing

Next stop, 30 Rock. 

That’s a wrap on Los Angeles, let’s move this show to the East Coast!

#musicmixer #kellyclarkson #thekellyclarksonshow #30rock

Sometimes you gotta mix where you can. Hotel bed, for the win!

I bring a mobile rig with me everywhere I go, just in case, and it came in handy, recently. 

#protools #musicmixer #mobile #hotel
Olive me loves love you. #olives

Huge shoutout to @audixmics for this PDX720 Signature Edition microphone. I can’t wait to throw some sound waves at it!  Thanks @partymelt for making this happen. 👊🏻 

I’m pretty dang excited about it… anybody wanna come sing into it? 

#audix #pdx720 #microphone #recordingstudio #newmusic

It’s out! This album is so good! I’m proud to have played a small part in the production of this album, and I’m thankful for the opportunity to work with so many talented people. 

There’s something for everyone on this record, so give it a listen. 

#newmusic #kellyclarkson #chemistry #recordingengineer

Want to add a little punch to your drums in the mix? Try adding a mic like this, and compress the snot out of it! 🥊 

I used this on @lesterestelle’s drums for the Kelly Clarkson Kellyoke EP. 

#drums #drumday #recordinghelp #mic #recordingstudio #kellyclarkson #kellyoke

Kick drum is always the first fader(s) I pull up. Maybe it’s the drummer in me, or just how I prefer, but it’s the backbone of the beat, so I make sure it’s right before I do anything else, mixwise. 

#avids6 #mixingconsole #faders #musicmixer

Back home in Nashville setting up the remote mix rig. I’m tired, but I’m excited… I think I look more tired than excited. Let’s go!
#musicmixer #homestudio #recordingstudio #nashville

Spending the day at Lambeau, cheering on my Packers!
#greenbaypackers #packers #gopackgo

How come @alanis doesn’t age? One of the photos is from 17 years ago, the other is not. She’s on @kellyclarksonshow today, telling stories and singing with Kelly, and mixing these performances definitely had me singing along. 👏🏼 
#alanis #alanismorissette #kellyclarkson #songsandstories

Late night mixes, creeping up on Halloween. I love my job… but I also love sleep. 

#protools #musicmixer #recordingstudio #studiogear #trackball

My younger brother Mark and I are wishing you a happy Halloween, from the 80’s. They never saw us coming… but they heard us. They definitely heard us. 

Y’all be safe out there!

🎃 👻 

#halloween #80sfashion #costumes #besthalloweencostume #retro #vampire

Late night mixing on Halloween 👻 

Rocking my @octobersveryown Packers jacket to keep warm in the studio. Go Pack Go! 
#packers #greenbaypackers #octobersveryown #ovo #recordingstudio #musicmixer

The fx rack in my home studio makes me so happy! I’ve got a few classics as well as a couple unique pieces, which make for a fun time. 

The Drew Expressor is really cool on loops and breaks, and the Quad Eight RV-10 is a spring reverb with a lot of character that I picked up from Pam Tillis. 

#outboardgear #reverb #lexicon #musicmixer #nashville

Waking up with the ability to see my family before work is a blessing. I’m thankful for the genius minds who developed the technology for me to mix @kellyclarksonshow, remotely, from my studio. 

I’m thankful for the team of people onsite at 30 Rock who make my job easy, and for those who trust me to mix their music. 

#thekellyclarksonshow #kellyclarkson #musicmixer #recordingstudio #30rock #remotework

This is Emmy number 3 for our team! It was great seeing their faces all in the same room… they’re like family. 

#redcarpet #emmy #daytimeemmys #soundmixing #thekellyclarksonshow
